{"@context": "https://schema.org", "@type": "JobPosting", "title": "Senior Backend Engineer", "description": "<p>Pogos is looking for a Senior Backend Engineer with strong Node.js expertise to join our growing team. AI-first development is part of our daily workflow, helping engineers design, build, and ship software faster and with higher quality.  You will work on a modern integration and automation platform that connects eCommerce, ERP, warehouse, and fulfillment systems, enabling merchants and operators to run complex commerce operations at scale.</p>

<p>In this role, you will design and build secure, scalable backend services and APIs that power our platform and support a growing global customer base.</p>
